; Keeper_attempt_liveness — runtime attempt streaming liveness boundary.
;
; Bundles the pure FSM, env/budget config, and Eio observer glue for one
; provider attempt. The parent keeper driver still references the bare
; Keeper_attempt_liveness* modules.
;
; (include_subdirs no) opts out of parent's (include_subdirs unqualified).
; (wrapped false) preserves the existing module names at call sites.
(include_subdirs no)

